# One scene, a whole wardrobe — noir is half of the light/dark PAIR:
# record the same tape under -dress noir and -dress paper and you have
# both assets a GitHub <picture prefers-color-scheme> needs.

Output noir.gif
# foley: dress noir

Set Width 700
Set Height 340
Set FontSize 16
Set TypingSpeed 35ms

Type "echo 'same tape, dressed as: noir'"
Enter
Sleep 1200ms
Type "seq 1 3"
Enter
Sleep 2s
